1. On *putuje* po celom svetu. (He travels around the world.) 
2. Ovaj voz *putuje* između Beograda i Novog Sada. (This train travels between Belgrade and Novi Sad.)
3. Kada *putuješ* avionom, treba da se pridržavaš svih propisa. (When you travel by plane, you should follow all the regulations.)
4. Marko *putuje* u inostranstvo radi posla. (Marko is traveling abroad for work.)
5. Mladi par *putuje* na egzotično ostrvo kako bi proslavili medeni mesec. (The young couple is traveling to an exotic island to celebrate their honeymoon.)
6. Kad god *putujem*, uvek ponesem svoju knjigu. (Whenever I travel, I always bring my book with me.)
7. Oni su *putovali* u Grčku prošle godine. (They traveled to Greece last year.)
8. Kako bi sačuvali uspomene, oni su *putovanje* dokumentovali fotografijama i snimcima. (To preserve memories, they documented their travels with photos and videos.)
9. Trenutno ne *putujem* mnogo zbog pandemije. (I'm not traveling much currently due to the pandemic.)
10. Iako je umoran od dugog putovanja, on *putuje* dalje ka svom odredištu. (Although tired from the long journey, he continues to travel towards his destination.)